name: Hidden Universe - Ro02 / by The Mogg
description:
The Hidden Universes want to be heard. Not even the strongest breath can stop the heartbeat of a planet. A flash of Light reflected in your eyes revealed  your galaxies fires, while the stars poured out of your skin. A heartbeat is calling us. Can you hear it? Let us keep the light of this meditation burning.

Ability: Higher Perception //// Element: Water //// Formula: Ro02(UN03)
